{"tid":1245544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[再整合] 所有29個功能界別 (連超區) 選民資格 (合共35席)","createTime":"2019-06-20T10:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T14:09:34.000Z","uid":262154,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"557916772c24ab74439e3278bc38205bda3eef3a","tid":1245544,"uid":262154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T10:49:32.000Z","msg":"可以去 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1243657/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1243657/</a> 爬文, 呢度只係再重整<br />\n或者去呢個EXCEL幫手UPDATE:<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1BEIuxzPT8gQ-9VJRlxkWqxdwyw1K3uCP/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1BEIuxzPT8gQ-9VJRlxkWqxdwyw1K3uCP%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=36274586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1BEIuxzPT8gQ-9VJRlxkWqxdwyw1K3uCP/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n首先搞清楚BASIC CONCEPT:<br />\n有分 <br />\na) 個人票 - 入左傳統功能界別就無得投超區 (超區有一百萬票, 傳統得幾百到幾千, 有得揀一定係傳統界別) <br />\nb) 團體票 (團體可以係組織, 公司, 機構, 公會等等), 團體票 即係成個團體有一票, 個團體會委任一個人代表成個團體<br />\n每個界別組成同坃法都唔同, 有啲有個人, 有啲有團體, 有啲兩樣都有, 請睇上面EXCEL, <br />\n<br />\n1) <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">再講多次，功能組別唔係一時三刻可以做選民，因為大部分都要成為左會員12個月/團體成立左12個月, 先可以登記做選民，所以下年好大機會趕唔切, 不過各位巴打可以做就盡快做, 因為今日做，2021年就可以係選委選舉投票，間接影響2022特首，今日唔做，慢慢淡左，4年後都係會趕唔切</span></strong><br />\n2) 種票係犯法, 但係所有界別嘅資格都係公開, 得就得, 唔得唔好勉強<br />\n3) 本身泛民已有既功能組別要keep番, 因為唔一定十拿九穩, 建制會不斷放入去搶<br />\n4) 無論如何都要投哂2票 (地區+功能) <br />\n<br />\n睇完上面EXCEL 可以考慮 下面幾個: <br />\nA. 邊D界別可以增加團體票 (eg 成立新機構), 就咁睇好似:<br />\n<br />\n1. 體育、演藝、文化及出版界<br />\na. 文化界 <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89/35165/%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%95%8C%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E5%A2%9E28-%E5%89%B5%E8%97%9D%E5%9C%98-%E8%B8%A2%E8%B5%B0%E9%A6%AC%E9%80%A2%E5%9C%8B-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E8%A9%95%E4%BC%B0%E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%2F35165%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25A2%259E28-%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%2597%259D%25E5%259C%2598-%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%2580%25A2%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A9%2595%25E4%25BC%25B0%25E&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=9846989d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89/35165/%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%95%8C%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E5%A2%9E28-%E5%89%B5%E8%97%9D%E5%9C%98-%E8%B8%A2%E8%B5%B0%E9%A6%AC%E9%80%A2%E5%9C%8B-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E8%A9%95%E4%BC%B0%E</a><br />\n<br />\nb. 體育界<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=578339132339132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D578339132339132&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=6ac61dab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=578339132339132</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 勞工界 - 開工會 - 最少7個同行業的人, 每年要核數,交報表<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1243403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1243403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 飲食界<br />\n - 所有食牌持有人, (可公司 / 個人)<br />\n<br />\nB. 邊D界可以搵多D個人票.例如<br />\n1. 工程界<br />\n2. 建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界<br />\n3. 地產及建造界<br />\n4. 進出口界<br />\n5. 紡織及製衣界 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242790/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242790/</a><br />\n6. 批發及零售界"},{"pid":"986b49cc3ef6e81d3ae4d4f0843c3b8b87d7d9c5","tid":1245544,"uid":6777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:27:41.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家多d 留意一下<br />\n現時<span style=\"color: red;\">推登記功能界別選民</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n議會同街頭同樣重要</span>！！唔好比班仆街分化我地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請share 比多d 人士</span>，唔該晒大家！！！<br />\n<br />\n如果你合資格請去登記<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">功能界別選票比超區更有用</span><br />\n<br />\n同埋share 埋比你<span style=\"color: red;\">相關既朋友同事</span><br />\n<br />\n有一兩個界別需要大家<span style=\"color: red;\">自發組隊去游說</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家可盡一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(重開) [整合] 所有29個功能界別選民資格 (合共35席)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243657</a><br />\n<br />\n[再整合] 所有29個功能界別 (連超區) 選民資格 (合共35席)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245544</a>"},{"pid":"ccab110f39fb816c4fd36226316cc2682876dbeb","tid":1245544,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:29:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日野餐係口罩上面寫+852 抗議黑警冇number</span></span>"},{"pid":"f5042b0a0cd22eb9dddde4105e8d4fb9920d4b31","tid":1245544,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"有關區選的<br />\n一齊幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[超長文]區議會fact check，點解要叫人做選民？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/daaHAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/daaHAS</a>"},{"pid":"620fcda308dd8efa0aff5a404288fea8ce447545","tid":1245544,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:31:23.000Z","msg":"［向五毛學習]五毛開post扮理性，鼓吹選舉無用，各派各屌，白票焦土，唔肯屌保皇，防止建制大敗。請大家用相同邏輯分化藍絲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251472\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251472</a>"},{"pid":"5db550f2864a99423bd24d5c42bcdaee73083f26","tid":1245544,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:31:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da824d3becc0e5f65d67fa2eb7d512b5289cd591","tid":1245544,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQXj8Ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQXj8Ad.jpg&h=cd49b3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家經歷過這兩星期的抗爭運動都辛苦了! 雖然「五大訴求」(包括埋「林鄭下台」)仍然未達到，但希望大家趁呢兩日先好好地休息，之後重新裝備再齊齊繼續抗爭吧~<br />\n<br />\n不過，有啲事就真係比較急嘅，就係 - <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">距離今屆新選民登記嘅截止日期<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>仲剩番10日咋</strong></span>!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你自己、兄弟姐妹、同事朋友等等仲未登記嘅，請好好把握今次嘅機會立即登記，以便喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">今年24/11嘅區議會選舉</span></ins></span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: pink;\">出年立法會選舉</span></ins></strong></span>，將一個一個賣港又冇立場嘅親共政棍跟尾狗狠狠地踢出議會，將議會嘅否決權還番俾人民吧!!!<br />\n(可惜嘅係，已登記選民嘅更改資料期限已經喺2/6結束了，但大家仍需要覆查自己嘅選民資料有冇俾人更改／刪除咗，尤其係最近換咗新身分證嘅朋友)<br />\n<br />\n有關選民登記嘅資料如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">《地方選區選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=c0f1df50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">《功能界別選民及／或選舉委員會界別分組選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=a1679841\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">網上更新電郵地址</span></strong> - <a href=\"https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/mainEM.jsp&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk%2Fosp%2Fra008%2FmainEM.jsp%E2%80%A6&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=09a630bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/mainEM.jsp&hellip;</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">選民資料網上查閱系統</span></span></strong> - <a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=dacd107a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n此外，資料組嘅朋友可以好好地利用呢段時間，儲齊呢段時間來班建制狗所做嘅「好人好事」並作出整理，成為「彈藥」以供文宣組嘅朋友製作長輩圖及其他文案等，對一眾被利用嘅中年／老人家作出「反洗腦」宣傳，辛苦大家了！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>＊＊＊ <span style=\"color: pink;\">齊心登記</span>，<span style=\"color: pink;\">一齊投票</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">用選票拆散保皇狗</span> ＊＊＊</strong></span>"},{"pid":"1a68f05500a3cc99a0daeb625a6997d0d8a87797","tid":1245544,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e044ef9658869b6b00dadcb40781329a4ad2476c","tid":1245544,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:45:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果大家可以呼籲埋小商店登記做飲食業既選民就更好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你我一人一呼籲就可以改變現況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家多d 留意一下<br />\n現時<span style=\"color: red;\">推登記功能界別選民</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n議會同街頭同樣重要</span>！！唔好比班仆街分化我地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請share 比多d 人士</span>，例如share 呢個msg 去<span style=\"color: red;\">十個post</span> 唔該晒大家！！！<br />\n<br />\n如果你合資格請去登記<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">功能界別選票比超區更有用</span><br />\n<br />\n同埋share 埋比你<span style=\"color: red;\">相關既朋友同事</span><br />\n<br />\n有一兩個界別需要大家<span style=\"color: red;\">自發組隊去游說</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家可盡一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(重開) [整合] 所有29個功能界別選民資格 (合共35席)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243657</a><br />\n<br />\n[再整合] 所有29個功能界別 (連超區) 選民資格 (合共35席)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245544</a>"},{"pid":"851a5f51d5f873d92a400f171b2b372027d29d88","tid":1245544,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9352477da032948b426004eb30b3cfda3f3dac4d","tid":1245544,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e0d1572a29e1d3134a2f44d35b91cfe54aea10e","tid":1245544,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008f5fbd8873d1899af04f75e422800f7f81fdef","tid":1245544,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7f8ce2401294bd3445f63e2ebf6096ef9e1833","tid":1245544,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:09:34.000Z","